Feature: Blog — post detail

  Scenario Outline: blog detail <slug>
    Given I navigate to "/blog/<slug>"
    Then "[data-testid=post-title]" should contain text "Post <i>:"
    Then "[data-testid=post-body]" should contain text "lorem ipsum"
    When I click "[data-testid=back-link]"
    Then "[data-testid=blog-title]" should be visible

